<p align="left">
In the cash book-overview, all revenues, expenditures and stock of days are displayed.<br />
<br />
In this overview, beginning inventory is equal to the sum you have registered as initial stock.<br />
Revenues / Expenditures are the totals. Revenues / Expenditures - Page are the totals for each page.<br />
<br />
By default, NOT Cancelled entries are displayed. To view other entries, then<br />
please click on the arrow symbols (up = NOT Cancelled, Down = Cancelled, right = Show all).<br />
You can also change the sorted order. Standard Sort by Date (newest entries first).<br />
<br />
Note:<br />
<br />
If no initial stock, be present, you will be prompted to enter a beginning inventory.<br />
<br />
Cash book entries can not be processed or deleted. Entries can be cancelled from the info page.<br />
(Administrator and User Group Manager and Root)<br />
